The Gadget Show was originally a technology preview and review show presented
by Jon Bentley, Jason Bradbury and Suzi Perry, but evolved over time to become
a more challenge based review program.

with only Jason Bradbury and Pollyanna Woodward as presenters.
 Series 18 was renamed again, this time to 'The All New Gadget Show', still
with Bradbury and Woodward as the only presenters.

the return of Jon Bentley and the addition of Countdown's Rachel Riley as
